folder: St. Mark's Avenue & Nostrand Avenue, Brooklyn, NY
original_title: Brooklyn: St. Mark's Avenue - Nostrand Avenue
text:
725 St. Mark's Ave., north side, between Nostrand and New York Aves., showing the home of the late Eugene O. Blackford, who at one time was State Commissioner of fish hatcheries, and New York's largest wholesale fish merchant.
May 29, 1929.
P. L. Sperr.
